{"tid":1248723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集體投訴] 犬隻挑釁示威者，可能干犯公眾地方內擾亂秩序行為","createTime":"2019-06-21T14:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T15:15:35.000Z","uid":36716,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cdc319a494bf37650b4e48718a54dce58668bd68","tid":1248723,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:02:58.000Z","msg":"第245章 《公安條例》 第17B條 公眾地方內擾亂秩序行為<br />\n(1)任何人在為某事情而召開的公眾聚集中作出擾亂秩序行為，或煽惑他人作出此種行為，以阻止處理該事情，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁12個月。<br />\n(2)任何人在公眾地方作出喧嘩或擾亂秩序的行為，或使用恐嚇性、辱罵性或侮辱性的言詞，或派發或展示任何載有此等言詞的文稿，意圖激使他人破壞社會安寧，或其上述行為相當可能會導致社會安寧破壞，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁12個月。<br />\n(編輯修訂&mdash;&mdash;2013年第1號編輯修訂紀錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/videos/2568587329820150/UzpfSTEwMDAxMzM0MzM1MDgxNzo3MDE1OTYxMjY5NjE4MjY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcantonese.rfa%2Fvideos%2F2568587329820150%2FUzpfSTEwMDAxMzM0MzM1MDgxNzo3MDE1OTYxMjY5NjE4MjY%2F&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDcnQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=c8094b2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cantonese.rfa/videos/2568587329820150/UzpfSTEwMDAxMzM0MzM1MDgxNzo3MDE1OTYxMjY5NjE4MjY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n投訴網址<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/ereport_details?report=CMPLNT_AGNST_POLICE_OFCR&amp;fontSize=100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.erc.police.gov.hk%2Fcmiserc%2FEGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI%2Fereport_details%3Freport%3DCMPLNT_AGNST_POLICE_OFCR%26fontSize%3D100&d=84TmSRyL%2BgXW7nGZFnhDcnQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=f2249ac3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/ereport_details?report=CMPLNT_AGNST_POLICE_OFCR&amp;fontSize=100</a>"},{"pid":"aa07f2c3f529734f95bdc2faf9df34e312227e9a","tid":1248723,"uid":36716,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"即使你唔敢出去<br />\n<br />\n齊齊去投訴,鍵戰都可以出一分力"},{"pid":"afc27145036a000693619ded2d619737226c760d","tid":1248723,"uid":101820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:05:45.000Z","msg":"個網嚇到廢埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7aea81beb6c830ffdae0cabc4e6039f6342596","tid":1248723,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"仲有無其他挑釁片段,我好似見到有個犬隻拎住個鏢鈀挑釁市民"},{"pid":"a53c2abfaab027ff8b9d19151aa48b51929efb7c","tid":1248723,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:06:52.000Z","msg":"盡公民責任"},{"pid":"1f39976c6ad950efeff938bea0ac065e97a977a1","tid":1248723,"uid":50998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:07:31.000Z","msg":"起碼要佢地開file"},{"pid":"e69dbd410d67c431676d9976dfee658ead1549b4","tid":1248723,"uid":36716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f39976c6ad950efeff938bea0ac065e97a977a1","tid":1248723,"uid":50998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:07:31.000Z","msg":"起碼要佢地開file"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:08:17.000Z","msg":"真,告唔告到未知,但佢挑釁市民一定有錯"},{"pid":"5b60bd921233aac0ab2c983c5d7dedf75af6eb78","tid":1248723,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:09:16.000Z","msg":"一哥開記者會時叫佢解釋下"},{"pid":"e60954209fdb84cfb91be5020641036d11a2f6ba","tid":1248723,"uid":261169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:09:31.000Z","msg":"個網又摺埋咗"},{"pid":"dbf140280a901ecab11fb43bbaf5ef04aa594ea1","tid":1248723,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"要留意下"},{"pid":"059c13f994fc687ef02974176b6985c66b47b713","tid":1248723,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b92d5a6656fc56998cb4472de8094be35a599c81","tid":1248723,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:53:12.000Z","msg":"一入去都未load完就服務逾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇咁撚廢呀"},{"pid":"03e561a20496c258bcad51c79114a5dfda9f9cbe","tid":1248723,"uid":79182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"大家記住 呢個係長期不合作運動<br />\n啲犬清場 我地唔使硬碰<br />\n唔好送人頭俾佢<br />\n我地返去休息 抖足精神 第二日又嚟過<br />\n我地不斷做 搞亂個社會秩序<br />\n然後同政府談判先係辦法<br />\n<br />\n千其唔好死衝 無意思㗎 <br />\n我地做咩都唔合法<br />\n警犬做咩都有政府撐腰<br />\n我真係唔想再有義士犧牲<br />\n<br />\n我知有人會諗 叫咗咁多人出嚟<br />\n咩都唔做咁on9?<br />\n無錯我地係人多 但我地和平遊行又試過<br />\n衝擊佔領又試過 有用咩??<br />\n要贏 一定要試新方法<br />\n一於試吓不合作運動啦"},{"pid":"2fa95890a19cfff5579943fec5c3ffe475dbfacb","tid":1248723,"uid":41861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa07f2c3f529734f95bdc2faf9df34e312227e9a","tid":1248723,"uid":36716,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"即使你唔敢出去<br />\n<br />\n齊齊去投訴,鍵戰都可以出一分力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"投訴有用??"},{"pid":"0fc7b761054af895f26fb06d2a793108ff689389","tid":1248723,"uid":224894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:56:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8655bb6e980acbee76963cf7fe0265f58afca5bb","tid":1248723,"uid":217761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a53c2abfaab027ff8b9d19151aa48b51929efb7c","tid":1248723,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:06:52.000Z","msg":"盡公民責任"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:10:26.000Z","msg":"警犬挑釁市民，已經係行為失當，可以投訴"},{"pid":"486651ad288966ed44610663d0cb466f50a3c142","tid":1248723,"uid":36716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8655bb6e980acbee76963cf7fe0265f58afca5bb","tid":1248723,"uid":217761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a53c2abfaab027ff8b9d19151aa48b51929efb7c","tid":1248723,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:06:52.000Z","msg":"盡公民責任"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T15:10:26.000Z","msg":"警犬挑釁市民，已經係行為失當，可以投訴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20